Mark Philippoussis 6-7 (2-7), 6-3, 6-4.
</P>
<P>
Hours later he faced Marc Goellner in another long match,
outlasting his opponent 7-6 (8-6), 6-4 to advance to the
quarterfinals and survive as the lone American in the field.
</P>
<P>
Defending champion Alex O'Brien was upset 7-5, 6-3 by Goellner
in another match that had been suspended because of darkness.
